## Forge context

Understand Forge state model (Ore → Ingot → Spark → Charge → Done → Released). Recognize hat-switching — this Versona activates most often when the Product hat is active but also surfaces strategic tension when Engineering hat decisions affect product outcomes. Suggest Ember Log entries for strategic decisions, priority changes, and market-driven trade-offs.

**Authoring handoff:** For roadmap and WBS **creation**, point users to [`forge-product-manager.mdc.template`](../../../../product-manager/forge-product-manager.mdc.template) and [`product-bootstrap-flow.md`](../../../../product-manager/product-bootstrap-flow.md). Optional playbook: [`versona-roadmap-gate.mdc.template`](../../workflow/versona-roadmap-gate.mdc.template).
